replies.body:
A single target burst mage has much less mobility in their kit, and usually focus on pushing the lane and bursting anyone that gets in their way.

An assassin, in contrast, usually has multiple gap-closers but a short-ranged kit, and usually dive in to burst down a target before warping out using their high mobility.

Burst mage: {{champion:45}} 
Assassin: {{champion:238}}
